text: Kanchura () is a rural locality (a village) in Shabagishsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 185 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Yermolayevo, 7 km from Shabagish. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Kanchura
